    slug: 'pub-crawl-bar-hopping-safety-guide',
    title: 'Pub Crawls and Bar Hopping: Staying Safe During Organised Drinking Events',
    category: 'Personal Safety',
    excerpt: 'Organised drinking events including pub crawls and bar hops are popular with students but carry specific risks that differ from a regular night out. A little preparation and awareness makes a significant difference.',
    metaDescription: 'Safety guide for pub crawls, bar hops, and organised drinking events for young adults. Covers pacing alcohol, group safety, drink spiking risks, and getting home safely from multi-venue nights.',
