    excerpt: 'Starting university while maintaining a long-distance relationship is a common and genuinely challenging situation. Understanding what makes these relationships succeed or fail helps you navigate this with greater clarity.',
    metaDescription: 'Practical advice for young adults in long-distance relationships at university. Covers communication strategies, maintaining independence, managing jealousy, and recognising when a relationship is no longer healthy.',
